# Cargo build output
/target
**/target

# Rustfmt backup files
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these for debugging
*.pdb
*.run

# cargo mutants — mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# Meson build directories. Convention is `builddir`; tolerate variants.
/builddir
/build
/_build

# Compiled GSettings schemas — produced by build.rs; the source XML
# is checked in but the binary blob is regenerated on every build.
data/gschemas.compiled

# Reference repos. Cloned manually, never pushed.
.netnewswire/
.newsflash/
.liferea/

# Memory-diagnostic capture file. Produced by `--debug` runs, regenerated
# every time, never committed.
debug-memory.log
